elements.2211.03198_8cac6d1560c84f7fdca3baa32f2e0: Gauge Theory plays a crucial role in many areas in science, including high energy physics, condensed matter physics and quantum information science
elements.2211.03198_255b236e53417e14e4e8b076c02a3: In quantum simulations of lattice gauge theory, an important step is to construct a wave function that obeys gauge symmetry
elements.2211.03198_806c9f7cc33c721abad4b991db1c7: In this paper, we have developed gauge equivariant neural network wave function techniques for simulating continuous-variable quantum lattice gauge theories in the Hamiltonian formulation
elements.2211.03198_02bf55ffe959fe4a3660b5ca84e81: We have applied the gauge equivariant neural network approach to find the ground state of
elements.2211.03198_157afd2306fb6c59bb473c685d3c8: -dimensional lattice gauge theory with U(1) gauge group using variational Monte Carlo
elements.2211.03198_e16d4133cd85fa2e72ebe92c2af53: We have benchmarked our approach against the state-of-the-art complex Gaussian wave functions, demonstrating improved performance in the strong coupling regime and comparable results in the weak coupling regime.
elements.2211.03198_041695508ebfb6ced3d48cd4683d8: Parametrized gauge equivariant functions play an increasingly important role in deep learning and the quantum simulation literature
elements.2211.03198_1422afa79c1d992b49920a352f252: The historical importance of gauge equivariance in physics literature originates from the gauge principle, according to which the action functional dictating the interactions of fundamental fields must be invariant under symmetry transformations that depend upon

elements.2211.03198_a946419836f8cfd310a0e4a926269: With the advancement of machine learning, neural networks have been proposed

elements.2211.03198_82100020c7c2f4b9a57b47377d81b: Gauge theories appear in a variety of contexts in physics, including high energy physics, condensed matter physics and quantum information science, and provides fundamental understandings of our universe
elements.2211.03198_e6467b3fc7f70f722cb65b04331f8: In this work, we have developed gauge equivariant neural networks for continuous-variable quantum lattice gauge theory with U(1) gauge group
elements.2211.03198_4cacee26fa6358d58bcb75a15f4f5: We have applied the approach to find the ground state of 2+1D U(1) pure gauge theory and demonstrated better performance in the strong coupling regime and comparable results in the weak coupling regime over the state-of-the-arts complex Gaussian wave function
elements.2211.03198_e18f428e495cf5b78e2f3b45d6a6b: This is an important step that goes beyond the discrete lattice gauge theory
elements.2211.03198_de213b6db24edeada80a77f7f91e7: and opens up the possibilities of simulating the ground state and real time dynamics of lattice gauge theories with different symmetry groups
elements.2211.03198_8e48f29b86f7f2368cce4657a3a76: Future research will generalize the approach to non-abelian lattice gauge theories and study important physics such as confinement.
